<FILEID>AP-NR-04-05-88 2338EDT</FILEID>
<1ST_LINE>r a AM-DigestBriefs     04-05 0978</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Digest Briefs,1015</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>Eds: This package does not contain the following items from the
News Digest: NICOSIA, Cyprus _ Hijack; MILWAUKEE _ Primary Rdp;
