and things could turn down, but there's no disaster here,'' he said.
   Analysts expect the Dow to remain in the narrow range, as trader
sentiment swings from recession fears to inflation paranoia.
   Among actively traded issues, Woolworth jumped 3} to 57~ after
rising 8~ in the previous session when Dart Group Corp. said it was
interested in acquiring a stake in the retailer.
