   Gainers slightly outnumbered losers by about 10 to 9 in the
overall tally of New York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 755
up, 709 down and 478 unchanged.
   Volume on the Big Board came to 108.59 million shares an hour
before the closing bell.
   The Dow pierced the 2,000 mark at midmorning but then met with
